title: Drawing, Design for Round Dining Table on Carved Bracket Feet, 1900–05
title_raw: Design for Round Dining Table on Carved Bracket Feet
inscribed: Inscribed in graphite, center top of image: 4'.6" Round top / 12'.0' Extension; at lower right of image with arrow pointing to right foot: carving; at lower left and lower center of sheet: ALTERN... / Dining Table
creditline: Gift of The Lake St. Louis Historical Society
description: Round molded top raised on plain columnar support with concentric molding around bottom, sitting atop "X"-shaped molded base terminating in 4 carved bracket feet with acanthus-leaf decorations.

participants.person_name: The Lake St. Louis Historical Society
